Get List of Labstep Protocols

getProtocols.Rd

This function allows you to search your Protocol library on Labstep.

getProtocols(user, count = 100)

Arguments

user

A labstep user object. Must contain an `api_key` field. Returned from `login` command
count

Number of results to return. Defaults to 100.

Value

Returns a list of `protocol` objects

Examples

user <- login("demo@labstep.com","demopassword")
protocols <- getProtocols(user)
print(protocols)
